JobSeek – Job Portal Website
JobSeek is a modern job portal web application that connects job seekers with employers.
It provides an intuitive interface for candidates to search and apply for jobs, and for employers to post and manage job listings easily.

🚀 Features
User Authentication – Sign up and log in for job seekers and employers.

Job Search & Filters – Search jobs by title, location, category, and more.

Responsive Design – Works seamlessly on desktop, tablet, and mobile.

Employer Dashboard – Post, edit, and delete job listings.

Job Seeker Dashboard – Save jobs, apply, and track applications.

Real-time Updates – Instant job posting and application status changes.

Secure & Scalable – Built with modern technologies ensuring performance.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend:

HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (React.js)

Material UI / Bootstrap (for styling)

Backend:

Node.js, Express.js

Database:

MongoDB / MySQL (based on your implementation)

Other Tools:

JWT Authentication

RESTful API

Git & GitHub for version control
